# Meta Competitor Ad Library

## Beginner local mode (SQLite)

You can run this app without Docker or PostgreSQL.

## Minimum install

1. Node.js 20+
2. npm

## Copy/paste commands in order

```bash
cp .env.example .env
npm install
npm run db:generate
npm run db:migrate
npm run db:seed
npm run verify:runtime
npm run dev

Then open:

http://localhost:3000

What works
Dashboard page with real seeded data
Ad detail page with a real saved analysed ad
Runtime verification script
Production note

SQLite is for local verification.
PostgreSQL template remains at prisma/schema.postgres.prisma.
